Open Street Map

Egypt, May-2021

Hany Nagaty

May-2021

Open Street Maps Description

This is a brief description for the data downloaded from Open Street Map website. OSM is described as “a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license”. I downloaded the data for Egypt on May-2021. I used this mirror.

The data has the below 16 layers

1. gis_osm_roads_free_1

This is the road network. It has classes such as motorway, primary, secondary, residential, …..etc.

Total number of line segments: 1660855.
